---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Joshua Song — JSong Realty | Atlanta REALTOR® with Keller Williams Realty"
  description="Meet Joshua Song — an Atlanta REALTOR® focused on clear data, careful negotiation, and real advocacy for buyers and sellers across Intown and metro Atlanta."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; About</nav>
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>Meet Joshua Song.</h1>
      <p>A REALTOR® who treats every transaction like the biggest one you'll ever make — because for most people, it is.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split split-about">
        <div class="reveal media-stack">
          <img src="/assets/img/joshua-portrait.jpg" alt="Joshua Song, REALTOR®" class="media-frame media-frame-portrait" width="600" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="media-note media-note-about">
            <span class="handwritten" style="font-size: 2rem;">Joshua</span>
            <p class="media-note-kicker">REALTOR® · Keller Williams Realty</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal delay-1">
          <span class="eyebrow">The short version</span>
          <h2>Atlanta roots, <span class="serif-italic">analytical approach.</span></h2>
          <p>I'm Joshua — an Atlanta REALTOR® with <strong data-brand-brokerage>Keller Williams Realty</strong>. I work across Intown and the broader metro, with a focus on giving clients the same quality of information I'd want if I were sitting on their side of the table.</p>
          <p>My practice is built on three commitments: verified data, clear communication, and calm, disciplined negotiation. Real estate is deeply personal — my role is to bring order, clarity, and confidence to every step of it.</p>
          <p>Outside of real estate, you'll find me exploring Atlanta's neighborhoods on foot, supporting the coffee shops of Virginia-Highland, and holding to a simple belief: the best transaction is one both sides feel good about.</p>
          <div class="hero-cta cta-gap-sm">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/listings/">See current listings </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">How I work</span>
        <h2>Three commitments to every client.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="feature reveal">
          <span class="feature-num">01</span>
          <h3>Verified information, always</h3>
          <p>Square footage, permitted work, tax history, school zones — verified before we ever book a showing, so every decision is made on facts rather than assumptions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature reveal delay-1">
          <span class="feature-num">02</span>
          <h3>Responsive communication</h3>
          <p>Weekday calls, texts, and emails answered within the hour. You'll always know where we stand, what comes next, and why — in plain language.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature reveal delay-2">
          <span class="feature-num">03</span>
          <h3>Principled negotiation</h3>
          <p>Every negotiation is approached with preparation and composure — protecting your interests at every turn. Strategy first, always.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Client reviews</span>
        <h2>What clients say.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reviews-grid" data-reviews-grid data-reviews-limit="3"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band reveal">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Let's talk</span>
          <h2>About your next move.</h2>
          <p>Whether you're buying, selling, or simply curious about your home's value — the conversation is always welcome.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" href="/contact/">Start a conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
